item.description: Rain Magic By Erle Stanley Gardner Novelette–Complete FACT OR FICTION RAIN MAGIC is a most unusual story; it is one of those tales that leave something in the reader’s mind to think about-something on which his opin- ion is as good as any one else’s–as good as that of the author himself.
